tree-sitter-toml grammar sources
=================================

Origin: https://github.com/mattmassicotte/tree-sitter-toml
Branch: feature/spm
Commit: bf4ceeb9c7e3ef796106d7b8c481d539b653d3d8

The grammar sources in src/ (parser.c, scanner.c) and the Swift binding
header in bindings/swift/TreeSitterTOML/toml.h are vendored here because
the upstream feature/spm branch's Package.swift omits scanner.c from the
sources list, causing undefined-symbol link errors. This local target
includes both parser.c and scanner.c as required.

Upstream license: MIT (see https://github.com/mattmassicotte/tree-sitter-toml/blob/main/LICENSE)
Upstream grammar origin: ikatyang/tree-sitter-toml (MIT)

Modifications: None to the grammar sources or headers. The Package.swift
declaration is replaced by this local SPM target in MoonSwift's manifest.

This bundling is a workaround. The preferred long-term path is a fixed
upstream Package.swift (PR filed or fork maintained). When a working
external package is available, this local target should be removed and
the dependency entry in Package.swift updated to reference it.
